name: DailyChore
0:
”Alexa, daily chore”
”Alexa, open daily chore and tell me what I should do today”
”Alexa, open daily chore and give me a chore”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: daily chore
des: We all make chore lists, however we don't always check them. This skill will give you a new each day of the week. If you invoke the skill everyday you will complete all of the chores you should complete weekly.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
